The paper focuses on the analysis of hands in egocentric vision, which involves computer vision and human-computer interaction. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the development of human-computer interfaces, which falls under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of egocentric vision for robotics (cs.RO), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications.
